## Summary
This documentation explains Amplitude Experiment's sticky bucketing feature for feature experiments, which maintains consistent variant assignments for users even when experiment targeting criteria, percentage rollout, or rollout weights change, and includes configuration steps, use cases, and debugging methods using Experiment Assignment events.

